### ZeMeow API - Testes

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminApiKey = test123
@sessionId = {{createSession.response.body.session.id}}
@messageId = {{sendMessageText.response.body.message_id}}

## Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

## Criar Sessão (requer API Key global)
# @name createSession
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

{
  "name": "Test Session",
  "webhook": "https://webhook.site/test"
}

###

## Listar Todas as Sessões
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Obter Detalhes da Sessão
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Atualizar Sessão
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

{
  "name": "Updated Test Session",
  "webhook": "https://webhook.site/updated"
}

###

## Conectar Sessão (obter QR Code)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/qr
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Status da Sessão
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/status
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Estatísticas da Sessão
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/stats
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Enviar Mensagem de Texto
# @name sendMessageText
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/send/text
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

{
  "to": "+5511999999999",
  "text": "Olá! Esta é uma mensagem de teste da API ZeMeow.",
  "message_id": "msg_123456789"
}

###

## Enviar Mídia (imagem como exemplo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/send/media
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

{
  "to": "+5511999999999",
  "type": "image",
  "media": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mP8/5+hHgAHggJ/PchI7wAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "caption": "Imagem de teste"
}

###

## Enviar Localização
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/send/location
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

{
  "to": "+5511999999999",
  "latitude": -23.550520,
  "longitude": -46.633308,
  "name": "São Paulo"
}

###

## Enviar Contato
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/send/contact
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

{
  "to": "+5511999999999",
  "name": "Contato de Teste",
  "vcard": "BEGIN:VCARD\nVERSION:3.0\nFN:Contato de Teste\nTEL;TYPE=CELL:+5511999999999\nEND:VCARD"
}

###

## Desconectar Sessão
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/disconnect
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Logout da Sessão
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/logout
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}

###

## Deletar Sessão
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}
X-API-Key: {{adminApiKey}}